  <brief_title>Study of Mycobacterium w in BCG Refractory Superficial Transitional Cell Carcinoma of Bladder</brief_title>
  <acronym>STCC</acronym>
  <official_title>Open Label, Single Arm, Exploratory Phase I Clinical Trial to Evaluate Efficacy and Safety of Mycobacterium w (Mw) in BCG Refractory Superficial Transitional Cell Carcinoma</official_title>
