  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary purpose of this study is to evaluate the response rate of this treatment (Mw) in
      patients with BCG refractory superficial transitional cell carcinoma. Other objectives
      include detecting the effect of Mw on Time to Tumor progression and evaluating safety.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
